tasks - View your active task list
task - View full details of a specific task
done - Mark a task as completed
edit - Edit a task's title or due time
del - Delete a task
clear - Wipe all active tasks for a fresh start
opps - View all open opportunities and deadlines
opp - View full details of an opportunity
addobp - AI parse opportunity text/link (paste text after)
dopp - Mark an opportunity as applied or done
delopp - Delete an opportunity
remindme - Set a reminder (e.g. /remindme in 10 mins)
summary - Generate your weekly AI summary recap
settings - Change how your AI behaves or sounds
help - Get the full usage guide